  "Description": {
    "English": "A proteinous formation of unknown origin, replicated aboard the Space Anomaly. Its skeletal structure often retains pockets of air, leading to slightly warmer or cooler temperatures in the centre of the cage.<br><br>Provides decorative landscaping opportunities for bases.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种未知来源的蛋白物质，太空异象负责对其进行复制。它的骨骼结构之间存在一些气体，使得牢笼中心的温度相对表面较稳定。<br><br>可以作为基地的装饰景观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "來源不明的蛋白質構造，在太空異常上複製。其骨骼結構中常有空氣滯留，造成籠子的中心溫度較暖或較冷。<br><br>可為基地提供景觀美化的機會。"
  },
